results.name: Polylogarithm li(-n,-2/9) multiplied by (11^(n+1))/9.
comment: See the sequence A212846 which describes the general case of li(-n,-p/q). This sequence is obtained for p=2,q=9.
link: Stanislav Sykora, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..100
formula: See formula in A212846, setting p=2,q=9.
mathematica: f[n_] := PolyLog[-n, -2/9] 11^(n + 1)/9; f[0] = 1; Array[f, 20, 0] (* _Robert G. Wilson v_, Dec 25 2015 *)
